[0m[49m[38;5;9m- 161     [0m:[38;5;9m[49m | **CloudTrail** | Enabled: log all S3 and DynamoDB API calls. Allocation changes are auditable decisions. |
[0m[49m[38;5;9m- 162     [0m:[38;5;9m[49m | **Sample Data** | Synthetic OR utilization data. Generate from known distributions (case durations follow lognormal, volumes follow Poisson). Never use real surgeon names or patient data in dev. |
[0m[49m[38;5;9m- 163     [0m:[38;5;9m[49m | **Cost Estimate** | SageMaker Processing: ~$0.20/hour for ml.m5.xlarge (solve takes 5-30 min quarterly). Lambda: negligible for daily runs. DynamoDB: ~$25/month for on-demand. S3: negligible. QuickSight: $18-24/user/month. Total: $200-800/month depending on user count. |
