[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      161[0m:[38;5;10m[49m | **Encryption** | S3: SSE-KMS; DynamoDB: encryption at rest; all API calls over TLS |
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      162[0m:[38;5;10m[49m | **VPC** | Production: Lambda and Batch in VPC with endpoints for S3, DynamoDB |
