[0m[49m[39m  461, 473[0m:[39m[49m | Metric | Typical Value |
[0m[49m[39m  462, 474[0m:[39m[49m |--------|---------------|
[0m[49m[38;5;9m- 463     [0m:[38;5;9m[49m | Quarterly solve time | 30 seconds to 5 minutes |
[0m[49m[38;5;9m- 464     [0m:[38;5;9m[49m | Daily release solve time | < 500 milliseconds |
