[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      475[0m:[38;5;10m[49m | Solver time (20 ORs, 15 services) | 5-30 minutes |
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      476[0m:[38;5;10m[49m | Optimality gap | < 2% typically achievable |
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      477[0m:[38;5;10m[49m | Utilization improvement over manual | 5-15 percentage points |
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      478[0m:[38;5;10m[49m | Block release decision time | < 2 seconds |
